WEBVTT

00:51.200 --> 00:52.460
Why is it blurry again?

01:20.280 --> 01:22.000
Xiao Wuyi. It's wrong!

01:22.160 --> 01:22.910
Xie Jiayu.

01:23.560 --> 01:25.510
Xie Jiayu. I was almost killed.

01:26.530 --> 01:28.710
The stirrup you designed
is not flexible enough.

01:28.710 --> 01:30.230
It is called a slipknot.

01:30.590 --> 01:31.710
The harder you pull, the tighter it gets.

01:31.710 --> 01:33.280
If you don't use force,
it naturally loosens.

01:33.280 --> 01:34.680
Anmin's leg is weak,

01:34.680 --> 01:35.940
so he won't be dragged.

01:36.120 --> 01:37.979
I was rushing to tell you the news.

01:38.920 --> 01:39.920
But a remarkable person has arrived

01:39.920 --> 01:40.759
at the Beifu Army Camp.

01:40.759 --> 01:42.020
-And that...
-Shut up.

01:42.350 --> 01:43.280
You're so noisy.

01:47.070 --> 01:49.130
Xiao Wuyi, you're throwing up blood.

01:49.630 --> 01:50.560
You're hurt?

01:50.560 --> 01:51.620
Where are you hurt?

01:53.150 --> 01:53.950
Tell me!

02:02.870 --> 02:03.760
You're blind?

02:06.570 --> 02:07.710
If you let anyone know

02:07.710 --> 02:08.630
that there's something wrong with my eyes,

02:08.630 --> 02:09.710
I'll kill you now.

02:10.120 --> 02:10.710
What?

02:10.710 --> 02:12.970
And I'll destroy your Miraculous Craft.

02:16.120 --> 02:16.560
I...

02:17.310 --> 02:19.150
We will put our lives on the line

02:19.150 --> 02:20.430
to help His Highness
win the three provinces.

02:20.430 --> 02:21.310
With His Highness leading the way,

02:21.310 --> 02:22.190
we won't lose.

02:22.400 --> 02:25.400
Yes, with His Highness here,
everything will be fine.

02:25.750 --> 02:26.680
What's going on?

02:30.400 --> 02:31.520
Hold my waist tight.

02:31.520 --> 02:32.920
I'll get you on the horse.

02:41.560 --> 02:42.760
Keep your voice down.

02:53.190 --> 02:54.360
If you trust me,

02:54.490 --> 02:55.620
just hold the reins.

02:56.079 --> 02:57.240
Let me be your eyes.

03:00.560 --> 03:01.120
Okay.

03:03.030 --> 03:04.470
I'm taking Xiao Wuyi with me.

03:04.470 --> 03:05.330
Your Highness.

03:05.360 --> 03:06.120
On our wedding night,

03:06.120 --> 03:08.470
he promised to teach me to ride
and enjoy the scenery.

03:08.470 --> 03:10.360
But these days he's been busy
either with reforms

03:10.360 --> 03:11.480
or with peace talks.

03:11.480 --> 03:13.400
No one knows whether he'll survive
in the competition.

03:13.400 --> 03:15.150
I don't want to be a young widow.

03:16.120 --> 03:17.250
So today, he is mine.

03:17.290 --> 03:19.090
I'll return him to you tomorrow.

04:48.730 --> 04:52.750
[Key to the Phoenix Heart]

04:53.120 --> 04:55.650
[Episode 9]

04:55.720 --> 04:57.990
[Prince Jing'an's Mansion]

05:01.120 --> 05:04.160
I don't know when you'll regain
your sight this time.

05:04.830 --> 05:06.690
Or I might never see again, right?

05:06.870 --> 05:07.430
Yes.

05:08.030 --> 05:09.830
You were badly injured at Jiuzhang Plain?

05:09.830 --> 05:10.920
You're almost blind.

05:10.920 --> 05:12.190
Yet you insist on messing with reforms

05:12.190 --> 05:13.120
and peace talks,

05:13.120 --> 05:14.750
even taking the field yourself.

05:14.750 --> 05:16.560
You are a lunatic.

05:16.630 --> 05:20.030
Last time you mentioned a strong medicine
that could cure me.

05:20.270 --> 05:21.530
It will be very painful

05:21.600 --> 05:23.400
and will shorten your lifespan.

05:25.750 --> 05:26.360
Use it.

05:26.950 --> 05:28.480
I can't lose in the competition.

05:28.480 --> 05:29.070
Wait.

05:29.560 --> 05:30.240
Um...

05:30.240 --> 05:31.720
Do you really not need to

05:31.720 --> 05:32.560
see another doctor?

05:32.560 --> 05:34.159
Ruisheng is the best doctor.

05:35.800 --> 05:36.310
Come on.

05:37.720 --> 05:39.680
It will be painful. Hang in there.

06:16.270 --> 06:17.670
The acupuncture is done.

06:17.720 --> 06:19.850
But it will get increasingly painful.

06:20.310 --> 06:22.160
Jiayu, just say something

06:22.510 --> 06:24.070
to distract him.

06:24.430 --> 06:25.510
What can I say?

06:25.920 --> 06:27.180
Say whatever you like.

06:28.920 --> 06:29.510
Then...

06:30.190 --> 06:30.920
Then, let me tell you

06:30.920 --> 06:32.110
the story of Mao and me.

06:32.110 --> 06:33.270
You'd better not speak.

06:33.270 --> 06:34.310
How can that be?

06:34.310 --> 06:35.310
I have to save you.

06:37.430 --> 06:38.310
I'll tell you

06:38.630 --> 06:40.120
the first time I met Mao.

06:41.390 --> 06:43.040
He was skinny back then.

06:43.630 --> 06:45.560
Father brought him to me and said

06:45.950 --> 06:47.950
Mao would be his student from then on.

06:47.950 --> 06:49.680
But I disliked Mao at that time,

06:50.159 --> 06:52.420
because I felt he stole my father from me.

06:52.560 --> 06:53.750
I preferred Lejun.

06:55.600 --> 06:58.240
But after Mao returned
from his study tour,

06:58.720 --> 07:00.390
I found he was so elegant,

07:00.390 --> 07:01.360
charming,

07:01.360 --> 07:02.310
and handsome.

07:02.310 --> 07:03.110
Superficial.

07:03.560 --> 07:04.560
You know nothing.

07:08.360 --> 07:09.490
Mao was so kind to me.

07:09.830 --> 07:11.040
When I sneaked out to play,

07:11.040 --> 07:12.630
he would catch me at the foot of the wall.

07:12.630 --> 07:14.430
I said I liked pear blossom candy.

07:14.430 --> 07:15.560
He went buy it for me.

07:16.070 --> 07:17.800
I said I wanted to see the world.

07:17.920 --> 07:19.870
He said he also enjoyed traveling around.

07:19.870 --> 07:21.920
I felt like

07:21.920 --> 07:23.800
God knew what kind of man I liked,

07:24.070 --> 07:26.240
so he specially made Mao the way I wanted

07:26.240 --> 07:27.240
and sent him to me.

07:27.270 --> 07:28.920
In short, in this world,

07:28.920 --> 07:30.650
there is no better man than Mao.

07:31.430 --> 07:32.240
I'm done.

07:32.270 --> 07:33.270
What do you think?

07:37.240 --> 07:38.770
Why don't you say anything?

07:39.240 --> 07:40.240
What should I say?

07:40.560 --> 07:41.760
Give me your opinion.

07:43.040 --> 07:44.100
Congratulations.

07:45.480 --> 07:47.430
What a pity. If it weren't for you,

07:47.560 --> 07:48.750
I would have married Mao long ago.

07:48.750 --> 07:49.950
If it weren't for me,

07:50.159 --> 07:52.890
you would have married
Prince Changsha long ago.

07:53.159 --> 07:54.560
That seems to make sense.

07:55.480 --> 07:57.240
Then, Mao and I should thank you.

07:57.240 --> 07:58.070
No need…

08:02.680 --> 08:03.830
I'll brew medicinal herbs.

08:03.830 --> 08:05.870
I'll be back in half a quarter
of an hour to remove the needles.

08:05.870 --> 08:06.480
Okay.

08:07.920 --> 08:08.510
Jiayu,

08:09.120 --> 08:11.720
say something to make him happy.

08:13.070 --> 08:15.120
Isn't my story with Mao pleasing?

08:17.390 --> 08:18.190
I understand.

08:19.160 --> 08:20.510
You are all alone.

08:20.630 --> 08:22.680
Hearing our mutual affection,

08:23.040 --> 08:24.480
you must be feeling unhappy, right?

08:24.480 --> 08:26.040
How am I all alone?

08:26.390 --> 08:27.070
Fine. Fine.

08:27.070 --> 08:28.130
I won't expose you.

08:28.510 --> 08:29.710
You'd better get out.

08:30.560 --> 08:31.830
Seeing you gives me a headache.

08:31.830 --> 08:33.429
Didn't you say you are blind?

08:35.120 --> 08:36.270
Why are you having a headache?

08:36.270 --> 08:38.400
Did Ruisheng mess up the acupuncture?

08:40.390 --> 08:41.150
Get out.

08:42.030 --> 08:42.600
Fine.

08:42.750 --> 08:43.750
I'll get out then.

08:47.720 --> 08:48.360
Ruisheng.

08:51.150 --> 08:52.840
His blindness must be kept a secret.

08:52.840 --> 08:53.720
I have to say he fell and

08:53.720 --> 08:55.790
got injured while riding horses
with me up the mountain

08:55.790 --> 08:57.450
and needs to rest for two days.

08:57.840 --> 08:59.240
It is not advisable to move him tonight.

08:59.240 --> 09:00.390
Will you or I watch him?

09:00.390 --> 09:02.250
-How about…
-Okay, you watch him.

09:02.630 --> 09:04.760
I have to go study his medical records.

09:06.020 --> 09:06.620
Ruisheng.

09:09.960 --> 09:11.480
Xiao Wuyi had a bad temper.

09:11.480 --> 09:12.960
How am I supposed to take care of him?

09:12.960 --> 09:14.620
Besides, I need to sleep, too.

09:14.720 --> 09:16.030
I even snore when I sleep.

09:16.030 --> 09:17.030
His Highness joined the army at fifteen.

09:17.030 --> 09:17.790
He lived rough

09:17.790 --> 09:18.960
and was used to a hard life.

09:18.960 --> 09:19.960
Even thunder wouldn't bother

09:19.960 --> 09:21.270
him, let alone snoring.

09:21.270 --> 09:22.720
Just give him some food and water
when he wakes up.

09:22.720 --> 09:24.320
It's easy to take care of him.

09:25.480 --> 09:27.630
Then, what does he like to eat?

09:27.750 --> 09:28.610
Hawthorn cake.

09:28.630 --> 09:29.750
He loves sour food.

09:31.270 --> 09:33.120
Can't you two take care of him?

09:33.360 --> 09:34.390
Now that His Highness is sick,

09:34.390 --> 09:35.790
we need to lead the Beifu Army

09:35.790 --> 09:36.550
to practice tactics for him.

09:36.550 --> 09:37.150
We can't get away.

09:37.150 --> 09:37.910
And his illness

09:37.910 --> 09:40.030
is partly because of
testing your stirrups.

09:40.030 --> 09:41.890
You need to take responsibility.

09:42.150 --> 09:42.870
Fine.

09:50.390 --> 09:51.000
Anmin!

09:52.390 --> 09:52.920
Hurry up!

09:55.480 --> 09:56.150
Run!

09:57.360 --> 09:58.080
Anmin!

10:00.910 --> 10:01.600
Mother!

10:02.390 --> 10:03.240
Xiao Wuyi.

10:04.270 --> 10:05.600
A man like you also feels

10:06.150 --> 10:08.150
scared and restless in your dreams?

10:13.320 --> 10:13.960
Mother!

10:19.720 --> 10:20.360
Mother!

10:27.080 --> 10:27.840
Anmin!

10:31.440 --> 10:33.570
Aren't you the one who didn't let Anmin

10:34.080 --> 10:35.340
go to the battlefield?

10:41.120 --> 10:42.780
Xie Jiayu, what are you doing?

10:44.870 --> 10:47.790
My Lady, someone left a bottle of
medicine at the door.

10:47.790 --> 10:49.320
I think it was the Princess.

10:56.320 --> 10:57.180
Your Highness,

11:00.440 --> 11:02.440
why don't you go in and see Xiao Wuyi?

11:05.120 --> 11:07.270
Don't you want to know
how badly he is injured,

11:07.270 --> 11:09.910
or who he called out to in his dreams?

11:14.550 --> 11:16.270
Wuyi keeps things to himself.

11:16.870 --> 11:18.000
If he doesn't want to say it,

11:18.000 --> 11:20.390
it's not appropriate for me to ask.

11:21.960 --> 11:24.670
I used to think my mother was too strict.

11:25.270 --> 11:28.600
Later, I realized it was because
she cared about me too much.

11:29.670 --> 11:31.360
If my mother knew I was sick,

11:31.910 --> 11:33.200
she would definitely stay by my bed

11:33.200 --> 11:34.600
and wait for me to wake up.

11:35.960 --> 11:36.820
Your Highness.

11:38.150 --> 11:39.550
I don't know what happened

11:39.550 --> 11:41.010
between you and Xiao Wuyi,

11:41.510 --> 11:43.440
and why you are estranged from him.

11:45.910 --> 11:47.310
But just now in his dream,

11:48.150 --> 11:50.280
he was clearly calling for his mother.

11:51.750 --> 11:54.680
A child who doesn't cry out in pain
may also be in pain.

11:54.750 --> 11:56.320
Now that you are worrying about him,

11:56.320 --> 11:58.120
why don't you tell him directly?

12:05.080 --> 12:06.910
I think when he wakes up at midnight,

12:06.910 --> 12:08.770
he'll want a bowl of chicken soup.

12:09.910 --> 12:10.770
Your Highness,

12:11.750 --> 12:13.410
could you teach me how to cook?

12:38.480 --> 12:41.010
Why is one side still thick
and the other thin?

12:41.790 --> 12:43.990
Because you are used to your right hand.

12:44.320 --> 12:46.120
Your right hand applies more force,

12:46.120 --> 12:47.580
while your left hand less.

12:47.960 --> 12:48.910
That's why.

12:49.440 --> 12:51.320
You're awake. Can you see?

12:53.960 --> 12:54.840
I heard it.

13:06.670 --> 13:07.530
Hawthorn cake?

13:07.750 --> 13:09.510
Xiao Wuyi, except for being blind,

13:09.510 --> 13:11.510
your other four senses are amazing.

13:11.960 --> 13:14.420
There's also chicken soup.
It's warming up.

13:19.670 --> 13:20.840
It's sourer than last time.

13:20.840 --> 13:22.120
I know you like sour food,

13:22.120 --> 13:23.580
so I didn't put much sugar.

13:26.150 --> 13:27.610
You made specially for me?

13:27.630 --> 13:29.020
I don't like hawthorn cake,

13:29.020 --> 13:30.620
and there's no one else here.

13:30.750 --> 13:31.360
Eat it.

13:43.120 --> 13:45.850
Try knocking five more times
with your left hand.

13:54.360 --> 13:55.960
Xiao Wuyi, you're amazing.

13:56.480 --> 13:57.960
You can tell just by listening

13:57.960 --> 13:59.360
which hand I'm using?

14:00.640 --> 14:01.400
Try it.

14:05.480 --> 14:06.030
Right.

14:12.150 --> 14:12.600
Right.

14:18.240 --> 14:19.750
Right hand knocked three times
on the left,

14:19.750 --> 14:20.910
left hand five times on the right.

14:20.910 --> 14:22.170
You can even hear that?

14:22.360 --> 14:23.620
Your force was uneven.

14:23.970 --> 14:27.360
The force was smaller when your left hand
knocked on the right.

14:27.360 --> 14:28.600
Just now, you only knocked a few times,

14:28.600 --> 14:30.080
so the contrast wasn't obvious.

14:30.080 --> 14:31.240
When both your hands

14:31.480 --> 14:32.940
moved smoothly together,

14:33.030 --> 14:35.440
the difference in force
was more obvious.

14:36.030 --> 14:37.910
The sounds of war drums
vary in intensity and tempo.

14:37.910 --> 14:38.840
That's how it is.

14:41.720 --> 14:43.840
You made new stirrups and saddles
for Anmin?

14:43.840 --> 14:45.370
The leather smells strong.

14:45.970 --> 14:46.610
Yes.

14:56.480 --> 14:57.750
Stop thinking about it for now.

14:57.750 --> 14:58.720
Try the soup.

15:05.120 --> 15:05.960
This is...

15:06.270 --> 15:07.320
I went to the Princess' courtyard,

15:07.320 --> 15:08.960
picked the liveliest old hen,

15:08.960 --> 15:10.420
and let her stew it for you.

15:10.550 --> 15:11.240
Is it good?

15:14.510 --> 15:17.750
I think Dowager Princess cares of you.

15:18.630 --> 15:20.390
She wouldn't hate you

15:20.390 --> 15:22.190
because of Anmin's leg, either.

15:22.480 --> 15:25.270
You should talk sincerely to your mom,

15:25.660 --> 15:27.720
instead of asking her in your dreams.

15:34.360 --> 15:35.030
Xie Jiayu.

15:35.550 --> 15:36.630
Do you love me?

15:38.440 --> 15:39.300
I'm asking you.

15:40.870 --> 15:42.080
Do you love me?

15:42.910 --> 15:44.270
What nonsense are you talking about?

15:44.270 --> 15:45.330
Now that you don't,

15:45.470 --> 15:46.960
then who do you think you are to me?

15:46.960 --> 15:48.030
Did you forget

15:48.030 --> 15:49.440
the warnings I gave you before?

15:49.440 --> 15:51.270
It's okay that you care about Anmin's leg.

15:51.270 --> 15:53.000
But now you are meddling with
my relationship with my mother.

15:53.000 --> 15:54.550
No one in the mansion cares about it.

15:54.550 --> 15:56.280
What does it have to do with you?

15:56.440 --> 15:57.870
It's none of your business!

15:57.870 --> 15:58.790
Do you really want to stay

15:58.790 --> 16:00.930
in the Prince Jing'an's Mansion
for the rest of your life?

16:00.930 --> 16:02.840
Then, I can make that happen for you.

16:02.840 --> 16:04.320
I take care of you because you are blind

16:04.320 --> 16:05.840
and can't take care of yourself.

16:05.840 --> 16:06.960
Otherwise, I won't care about you.

16:06.960 --> 16:08.020
Do I need your care?

16:08.360 --> 16:09.000
Fine.

16:09.750 --> 16:10.630
You don't.

16:11.270 --> 16:13.330
You mistake my kindness for ill will.

16:22.910 --> 16:23.630
Come out.

16:28.360 --> 16:31.890
If you have nothing to do,
take ten strokes of the military cane.

16:32.360 --> 16:32.870
Yes.

16:38.030 --> 16:38.690
Put it down.

16:59.670 --> 17:01.720
My Lady, don't be angry.

17:07.880 --> 17:09.010
Where is this place?

17:09.480 --> 17:12.410
Why am I still in Wensheng Yard
after walking around?

17:13.240 --> 17:13.790
My Lady,

17:14.680 --> 17:16.410
Isn't it good that His Highness

17:16.440 --> 17:18.030
doesn't want you to
meddle in his business?

17:18.030 --> 17:19.480
Why are you so angry?

17:19.960 --> 17:21.819
What exactly are you angry about?

17:22.240 --> 17:23.440
What am I angry about?

17:23.550 --> 17:25.720
I'm mad that he threw my good intentions
back in my face.

17:25.720 --> 17:27.780
My hawthorn cakes were wasted on him.

17:30.200 --> 17:30.750
Let's go.

17:32.750 --> 17:33.750
Ruisheng.

17:35.240 --> 17:37.370
Did something happen to His Highness?

17:38.680 --> 17:39.680
Nothing happened to him.

17:39.680 --> 17:41.410
I left because he made me angry.

17:42.480 --> 17:44.830
Ruisheng, how do you put up with him?

17:47.590 --> 17:49.640
His Highness seems strict and eccentric,

17:49.640 --> 17:51.570
but actually, he has a good temper.

17:52.310 --> 17:53.480
A good temper?

17:54.920 --> 17:56.850
A little moodiness doesn't count,

17:56.880 --> 17:59.880
especially when it's just towards
those close to him.

18:04.310 --> 18:05.110
Then, tell me,

18:05.350 --> 18:07.750
what kind of person is Xiao Wuyi
in your eyes?

18:07.750 --> 18:11.410
A monster who takes women by force
and neglects his rightful wife?

18:12.350 --> 18:13.440
Not exactly.

18:15.110 --> 18:17.440
There was that misunderstanding before,

18:17.830 --> 18:18.750
but later,

18:19.270 --> 18:20.680
I saw what you and Yuanji

18:20.680 --> 18:22.080
wrote on the prayer tree.

18:22.720 --> 18:23.790
Ziqi isn't...

18:28.400 --> 18:29.930
You already know part of it,

18:30.030 --> 18:31.310
but you don't know

18:31.720 --> 18:32.680
the rest.

18:32.960 --> 18:34.960
The name you saw on the prayer tablet

18:35.070 --> 18:36.070
was my husband's.

18:36.640 --> 18:38.070
He was Xiao Wuyi's Lieutenant General,

18:38.070 --> 18:39.670
who died defending the city.

18:39.920 --> 18:41.110
When the city fell,

18:41.350 --> 18:42.830
I was serving as a military doctor.

18:42.830 --> 18:43.960
I was captured by the enemy

18:43.960 --> 18:45.200
and held for over a month.

18:45.200 --> 18:47.860
Later, Xiao Wuyi arrived
with reinforcements,

18:48.030 --> 18:48.960
retook the city,

18:49.030 --> 18:49.830
and found me.

18:50.480 --> 18:51.540
But not long after,

18:52.960 --> 18:54.420
I found out I was pregnant.

18:55.070 --> 18:57.070
Many people questioned my chastity

18:57.440 --> 18:59.440
and doubted the child's paternity.

18:59.960 --> 19:01.920
Both my husband's family and my own

19:02.160 --> 19:03.830
forced me to die with my husband.

19:03.830 --> 19:05.680
They refused to acknowledge this child.

19:05.680 --> 19:07.160
When Xiao Wuyi found me,

19:08.840 --> 19:11.640
I was already half-submerged
in a freezing river.

19:13.030 --> 19:14.510
So, you married Xiao Wuyi?

19:14.920 --> 19:17.120
He took the blame for taking me by force,

19:17.240 --> 19:20.040
shielding me from everyone's doubts
and threats.

19:20.790 --> 19:22.070
Who would dare provoke

19:22.270 --> 19:24.400
the notorious Heir of Prince Jing'an?

19:26.640 --> 19:28.440
Later, when I gave birth to Ziqi,

19:29.030 --> 19:30.030
Xiao Wuyi told me

19:30.270 --> 19:32.030
he could help us change our identities,

19:32.030 --> 19:33.000
stay away from Jiankang,

19:33.000 --> 19:34.000
and live in peace.

19:34.070 --> 19:35.880
Or we could stay,

19:36.240 --> 19:38.590
and Ziqi would become a child
of the Xiao family,

19:38.590 --> 19:40.110
and I could, like before,

19:40.440 --> 19:41.960
be a military doctor.

19:42.480 --> 19:43.680
You chose the latter.

19:44.070 --> 19:45.510
I wanted to be closer to

19:45.510 --> 19:46.970
where my husband is buried

19:47.720 --> 19:49.750
and save more people like him.

19:55.440 --> 19:56.510
If you ask me

19:57.070 --> 19:59.070
what kind of person His Highness is,

19:59.680 --> 20:00.440
I think

20:02.960 --> 20:04.020
he is a good person.

20:07.270 --> 20:07.880
Ruisheng.

20:08.590 --> 20:09.550
The one who truly

20:09.550 --> 20:11.680
doesn't want Anmin to
go to the battlefield

20:11.680 --> 20:13.280
is Dowager Princess, right?

20:18.310 --> 20:19.910
He'd rather play the villain

20:20.380 --> 20:21.710
than explain himself.

20:23.160 --> 20:24.480
What a strange person!

20:35.070 --> 20:36.310
You've confused me.

20:36.750 --> 20:38.380
I originally promised Ruisheng

20:38.380 --> 20:39.840
to watch over you tonight.

20:43.160 --> 20:44.570
I made the stirrups for Anmin

20:44.570 --> 20:45.350
because I couldn't bear to

20:45.350 --> 20:47.070
see such an ambitious young man

20:47.070 --> 20:48.830
feel inferior due to a disability

20:48.830 --> 20:50.360
and unable to move forward.

20:51.640 --> 20:53.070
So, whether you are here or not,

20:53.070 --> 20:54.070
I would help him.

20:55.750 --> 20:57.590
I interfere with you and Dowager Princess

20:57.590 --> 21:00.720
because I heard you calling
for your mother in your sleep,

21:00.720 --> 21:03.440
and I saw her secretly bringing
medicine to the door.

21:03.440 --> 21:05.440
I know you two care about each other,

21:05.510 --> 21:06.720
so I talked too much.

21:09.270 --> 21:10.240
Doing good deeds

21:10.830 --> 21:12.090
doesn't need a reason.

21:13.100 --> 21:15.830
♪ One glance stirs heart's doom,
near yet far ♪

21:14.270 --> 21:15.400
Besides, Xiao Wuyi,

21:15.920 --> 21:16.920
even without Mao,

21:16.050 --> 21:18.600
♪ This fleeting moment ♪

21:17.550 --> 21:18.960
I consider you a friend.

21:20.160 --> 21:21.350
Although I don't understand politics

21:20.300 --> 21:24.310
♪ Tugs the threads woven by fate ♪

21:21.830 --> 21:24.030
and disagree with many of your methods,

21:24.350 --> 21:27.640
I know you have the people in your heart.

21:24.480 --> 21:26.480
♪ Bound tight evermore ♪

21:28.440 --> 21:31.440
♪ Sharing all the years together ♪

21:29.110 --> 21:30.510
In the repeating crossbow case,

21:30.510 --> 21:31.680
you had ten thousand reasons

21:31.680 --> 21:33.030
to blame me.

21:31.850 --> 21:36.220
♪ Peace I find nowhere but by your side ♪

21:33.550 --> 21:34.640
But you didn't.

21:35.270 --> 21:37.550
You even cleared Miraculous Craft's name
in front of the Beifu soldiers,

21:36.810 --> 21:39.720
♪ Bear witness with our souls ♪

21:38.310 --> 21:40.510
so my years of hard work weren't wasted.

21:40.650 --> 21:43.470
♪ Fear no partings or wax and wane ♪

21:41.310 --> 21:43.880
Isn't that enough to make us friends?

21:44.990 --> 21:49.330
♪ You know me and decided to
live and die together ♪

21:49.350 --> 21:53.010
♪ Believe in my persistence that
I won't run away ♪

21:52.750 --> 21:53.920
But friendship

21:53.030 --> 21:57.170
♪ You know I'm unyielding ♪

21:54.350 --> 21:55.680
isn't a one-way street.

21:56.070 --> 21:57.960
Since you don't consider me
a friend in your heart

21:57.960 --> 21:58.920
and are so mean to me,

21:58.000 --> 22:00.920
♪ Don't give up or dodge ♪

21:59.110 --> 22:01.350
our friendship ends tonight.

22:01.520 --> 22:05.290
♪ You know me, seeing things
through from start to finish ♪

22:03.160 --> 22:04.480
After you regain your sight,

22:04.480 --> 22:06.830
we will go our separate ways.

22:05.810 --> 22:09.930
♪ You see my move
under rebellious cover ♪

22:10.190 --> 22:14.170
♪ You know me, I'm willing to be
with you till the end ♪

22:14.200 --> 22:18.130
♪ Burn the fire in my heart ♪

22:18.160 --> 22:22.360
♪ Sincere hearts remain as of old ♪

22:29.500 --> 22:30.710
[Honglu Temple]

22:36.160 --> 22:37.560
I'm sick of the food here.

22:37.880 --> 22:39.350
Bring something different tomorrow.

22:39.350 --> 22:40.610
Do you have Popo melon?

22:40.640 --> 22:41.900
I've never heard of it.

22:45.790 --> 22:46.990
Then, come in with me,

22:47.070 --> 22:48.400
and I'll draw it for you.

22:54.310 --> 22:56.920
It's strange.
They've been here for so many days,

22:56.920 --> 22:58.110
but they didn't leave the room,

22:58.110 --> 22:59.510
nor did they let anyone in.

22:59.510 --> 23:00.640
But they opened the door

23:00.640 --> 23:01.440
for a melon?

23:02.110 --> 23:03.240
How weird!

23:18.310 --> 23:20.720
My Lady. My Lady. My Lady.

23:22.920 --> 23:23.750
-What's wrong?
-My Lady.

23:23.750 --> 23:24.400
Bad news.

23:24.480 --> 23:26.410
Eagle King and Prince Qi came here.

23:26.960 --> 23:28.030
Why did they come?

23:29.290 --> 23:31.550
Xiao Wuyi hasn't regained his sight yet.

23:33.140 --> 23:34.010
Interesting.

23:36.400 --> 23:37.680
News travels fast.

23:38.480 --> 23:40.830
Even the next courtyard might not
know about my illness,

23:40.830 --> 23:43.160
but the royalty and Eagle King knew first.

23:49.880 --> 23:51.750
I heard His Highness was injured
while riding yesterday.

23:51.750 --> 23:52.770
With the competition approaching,

23:52.770 --> 23:55.790
I come to inquire about his illness by
order of His Majesty and Empress Dowager.

23:55.790 --> 23:59.200
And Eagle King worried that His Highness
might not be able to participate in,

23:59.200 --> 24:00.730
so he has also come to visit.

24:02.160 --> 24:03.480
No need to worry about, Your Highness.

24:03.480 --> 24:05.750
My son only suffered
a minor injury yesterday,

24:05.750 --> 24:06.880
not affecting the competition.

24:06.880 --> 24:08.940
Then why hasn't he come out to meet us?

24:09.680 --> 24:12.480
Did Wuyi stay in his
Secondary Consort's yard?

24:13.160 --> 24:14.160
Go hurry him up.

24:15.070 --> 24:16.480
Yes, Mother.

24:20.440 --> 24:22.310
Even heroes cannot resist a sweet lady.

24:22.310 --> 24:23.040
That's fine.

24:23.480 --> 24:25.110
I have prepared some gifts

24:25.240 --> 24:27.100
for the others of the Xiao family.

24:32.470 --> 24:35.310
This is carefully selected
for Young Master Yao.

24:42.640 --> 24:43.440
Mulian Yu!

24:44.550 --> 24:45.640
What do you mean?

24:45.830 --> 24:46.830
Isn't it fitting?

24:47.550 --> 24:48.640
I am very sorry

24:48.750 --> 24:50.810
that I have never fought against him.

24:51.550 --> 24:52.510
I heard that in the early years,

24:52.510 --> 24:54.680
Wuyi and Anmin both had
the talent of generals.

24:54.680 --> 24:55.810
On the battlefield,

24:55.920 --> 24:58.640
your military exploits never lost
to Xiao Wuyi's.

24:58.640 --> 24:59.400
What a pity.

24:59.720 --> 25:02.350
Now in the Northern Border,
people only know of Xiao Wuyi,

25:02.350 --> 25:03.590
but not of Xiao Anmin.

25:03.880 --> 25:04.640
Mu,

25:05.480 --> 25:07.740
you came here in the morning to offend us.

25:08.200 --> 25:11.160
You don't want to
have a peace talk at all.

25:11.480 --> 25:12.790
Since that's the case,

25:13.270 --> 25:15.270
no need to wait for any competition.

25:15.640 --> 25:17.790
Right now,

25:18.310 --> 25:19.600
let's fight to the death!

25:19.600 --> 25:20.120
Come on!

25:20.350 --> 25:20.950
Father.

25:33.880 --> 25:34.680
That's right.

25:35.610 --> 25:37.680
I am this lame hound.

25:38.700 --> 25:40.430
But how do you know

25:41.590 --> 25:43.070
that this lame hound

25:43.550 --> 25:46.280
will never have a day
to fight on the battlefield?

25:46.960 --> 25:48.290
Then let's wait and see.

25:56.440 --> 25:57.960
Gentlemen,

25:58.310 --> 25:59.480
His Highness has woken up

25:59.480 --> 26:01.680
and is waiting for you two in the garden.

26:03.110 --> 26:04.200
Guess where I am!

26:04.880 --> 26:06.350
Come on, here, catch me!

26:07.070 --> 26:08.480
You can't catch me, right?

26:08.480 --> 26:09.480
Guess which side I'm on.

26:09.480 --> 26:10.140
Right here.

26:15.680 --> 26:16.480
They are here.

26:17.510 --> 26:18.480
Stop!

26:20.310 --> 26:21.590
Over here. Where?

26:25.320 --> 26:25.990
I got you.

26:36.600 --> 26:37.790
Prince Qi?

26:39.620 --> 26:42.020
I apologize. My respects to Your Highness.

26:42.750 --> 26:44.200
I heard that you got injured,

26:44.200 --> 26:45.510
which worried me a lot.

26:45.880 --> 26:47.240
I'm afraid that
it might affect the competition.

26:47.240 --> 26:48.240
But now it seems

26:48.640 --> 26:49.970
that I worried too much.

26:50.510 --> 26:51.770
Your Highness's women

26:52.400 --> 26:53.600
are truly beautiful.

26:56.240 --> 26:57.240
This way, please.

27:11.470 --> 27:12.000
Let's go.

27:19.590 --> 27:20.680
Gentlemen,

27:21.200 --> 27:23.480
would you like to choose a dancer
or two to accompany you?

27:23.480 --> 27:24.160
No need.

27:25.270 --> 27:26.590
It's good that you're fine.

27:26.590 --> 27:28.240
In this way, I can return to the palace

27:28.240 --> 27:29.750
and report to His Majesty
and Empress Dowager.

27:29.750 --> 27:31.350
Why the rush, Your Highness?

27:31.750 --> 27:34.550
It's rare for Young Lord Xiao to be
in such a good mood.

27:34.550 --> 27:36.510
I also have some peace talk terms

27:36.750 --> 27:38.550
to discuss with Young Lord Xiao.

27:46.880 --> 27:48.410
What do you want to discuss?

27:52.510 --> 27:53.710
Political marriage.

27:55.240 --> 27:56.270
Political marriage?

27:56.270 --> 27:57.680
Young Lord Xiao, who do you think is

27:57.680 --> 28:00.160
the most suitable person
in Southern Ye now?

28:04.640 --> 28:06.350
I suppose you got it reversed.

28:06.960 --> 28:08.270
If there is to be a political marriage,

28:08.270 --> 28:10.600
your country should send a princess to Ye.

28:11.880 --> 28:14.140
But it's too early to talk about this now.

28:14.440 --> 28:15.640
During horseback archery,

28:15.640 --> 28:17.240
any accident can happen.

28:18.070 --> 28:20.070
No matter how well we talk today,

28:20.400 --> 28:23.400
everything is in vain

28:23.960 --> 28:25.750
if one of us dies in the competition.

28:25.750 --> 28:26.830
That's true.

28:31.680 --> 28:34.340
I heard that Southern Ye has
the Pitch-pot game.

28:34.550 --> 28:36.440
I have always been fascinated by it.

28:36.440 --> 28:38.920
Could you teach me about it today?

28:39.400 --> 28:40.310
I can teach you.

28:41.720 --> 28:43.120
I am asking His Highness,

28:43.310 --> 28:44.640
not you, his concubine.

28:45.790 --> 28:47.520
Actually, your Pitch-pot game

28:47.590 --> 28:49.960
is similar to our horseback archery.

28:50.070 --> 28:51.440
It's just that Northern Qin

28:51.440 --> 28:53.480
prefers things to be straightforward
and thrilling.

28:53.480 --> 28:56.030
So, we don't aim at pots or targets

28:57.110 --> 28:58.160
but at slaves,

28:58.680 --> 29:00.540
the prisoners of war we captured.

29:01.310 --> 29:03.200
We make the captured little slaves

29:03.200 --> 29:04.160
our targets,

29:04.440 --> 29:06.110
and let them flee in panic

29:06.480 --> 29:08.400
and kill each other to survive.

29:09.320 --> 29:11.440
They think as long as they escape
tonight's arrows,

29:11.440 --> 29:12.510
they can survive.

29:13.110 --> 29:14.310
But we know

29:14.680 --> 29:16.160
even if they win,

29:16.550 --> 29:19.350
they will become warriors chosen by fate

29:19.830 --> 29:22.640
and be sent to the battlefield,

29:23.070 --> 29:25.160
serving as bait in the front row,

29:26.070 --> 29:28.470
and dying under the arrows
of their own kin.

29:29.070 --> 29:31.510
This is the fate of Southern Ye prisoners.

29:42.110 --> 29:43.040
Don't be afraid.

30:04.920 --> 30:05.780
Your Highness.

30:14.680 --> 30:16.440
Pitch-pot game originates
from archery rituals.

30:16.440 --> 30:18.680
The thrower can neither overdo it,

30:19.070 --> 30:20.240
nor fall short.

30:20.480 --> 30:21.830
It takes the exact middle path,

30:21.830 --> 30:22.750
impartial and unbiased,

30:22.750 --> 30:23.750
which is the foundation of the way.

30:23.750 --> 30:25.440
Cultivating the mind and character

30:25.440 --> 30:28.040
is the reason
why Pitch-pot game thrives in Ye.

30:28.480 --> 30:30.740
How could it be for the thrill of killing?

30:37.830 --> 30:39.290
You frightened my beauty.

30:39.680 --> 30:41.610
This is no way for a guest to behave.

30:43.550 --> 30:44.480
My apology.

30:44.960 --> 30:47.490
However, in the upcoming
horseback archery,

30:48.030 --> 30:49.830
we do seek the thrill of killing.

30:50.440 --> 30:53.170
Young Lord Xiao, do not hold back.

30:53.720 --> 30:54.270
I won't.

30:56.690 --> 30:58.870
[Prince Jing'an's Mansion]

31:03.830 --> 31:05.920
Xiao Wuyi, your archery was so cool!

31:06.110 --> 31:07.680
How did you hear
the direction of that arrow?

31:07.680 --> 31:09.070
I can't even describe it.

31:09.070 --> 31:10.130
Locating by sound.

31:10.590 --> 31:12.070
This way, even if you really can't see,

31:12.070 --> 31:14.470
it won't affect your commanding in battle.

31:20.590 --> 31:21.520
Watch your step.

31:34.680 --> 31:35.350
Xiao Wuyi.

31:35.960 --> 31:38.290
Perhaps you think I'm not your friend yet.

31:39.480 --> 31:41.140
But I want to tell you a secret.

31:43.000 --> 31:45.160
I am not the Princess's
biological daughter,

31:45.160 --> 31:45.960
but an orphan

31:46.510 --> 31:48.570
she brought back from the orphanage.

31:50.720 --> 31:52.480
My father and mother both thought

31:52.480 --> 31:54.080
I had no childhood memories.

31:54.920 --> 31:57.550
But I clearly remember

31:58.070 --> 31:59.440
the face of the Northern Qin man

31:59.440 --> 32:01.240
who killed my biological parents.

32:01.240 --> 32:03.440
He has a full beard, braided hair,

32:04.030 --> 32:05.440
long eyebrows reaching his temples,

32:05.440 --> 32:06.920
and a mole on his cheek.

32:07.270 --> 32:08.800
If not for my mother's pity,

32:09.440 --> 32:10.240
I would be teased to death

32:10.240 --> 32:11.550
like the young slaves

32:11.640 --> 32:13.350
Eagle King mentioned.

32:15.030 --> 32:15.830
Xiao Wuyi.

32:17.570 --> 32:19.300
If you can beat Eagle King once,

32:19.370 --> 32:21.030
you can beat him a second time.

32:22.770 --> 32:25.010
In this competition, Beifu has to win,

32:25.880 --> 32:28.720
for all the orphans in the world.

32:32.550 --> 32:33.830
And you must be safe.

32:35.030 --> 32:36.030
A person like you

32:36.640 --> 32:38.440
is born to be on the battlefield,

32:38.680 --> 32:40.140
making everyone fear you.

32:44.270 --> 32:46.160
Alright, I promise you.

32:47.830 --> 32:48.760
My friend Jiayu.

32:52.640 --> 32:53.750
You can see me.

32:54.440 --> 32:56.100
Why didn't you say so earlier?

32:57.480 --> 32:59.080
When did you see everything?

33:01.680 --> 33:02.400
My Lady.

33:04.790 --> 33:05.650
Your Highness.

33:05.750 --> 33:07.310
Prince Qi is waiting outside.

33:07.310 --> 33:08.370
He wants to see you.

33:09.110 --> 33:09.590
Okay.

33:14.680 --> 33:15.540
Your Highness.

33:16.310 --> 33:18.240
Eagle King got the news so quickly.

33:19.750 --> 33:21.270
The secret spies of Northern Qin

33:21.270 --> 33:23.320
dare to infiltrate
the Prince Jing'an's Mansion.

33:23.320 --> 33:25.040
It's time to warn them.

33:26.310 --> 33:26.830
Yes.

33:30.160 --> 33:30.680
Mao.

33:31.030 --> 33:31.590
Yaoyao.

33:33.030 --> 33:34.270
What exactly happened to Wuyi?

33:34.270 --> 33:35.530
You guessed it, right?

33:35.750 --> 33:37.550
He fell off a horse and went blind.

33:37.550 --> 33:38.410
Can he recover?

33:38.680 --> 33:40.480
Will it affect the competition?

33:40.680 --> 33:41.480
Don't worry.

33:41.920 --> 33:42.820
It was a minor injury.

33:42.820 --> 33:44.020
He has recovered now.

33:44.350 --> 33:45.200
That's good.

33:46.000 --> 33:47.400
If he hadn't commanded the tactics,

33:47.400 --> 33:49.400
even the bravest warriors
would just be stragglers.

33:49.400 --> 33:50.730
He can't make mistakes.

33:52.400 --> 33:53.200
But today,

33:53.400 --> 33:55.380
why did Eagle King come so suddenly?

33:55.380 --> 33:56.440
He entered the palace early,

33:56.440 --> 33:57.300
came prepared,

33:57.350 --> 34:00.020
and forced me to come here and ask
about Wuyi's illness together.

34:00.020 --> 34:02.030
His purpose was to put on
such a good show.

34:02.030 --> 34:02.960
Wuyi is right.

34:03.240 --> 34:06.480
He just wants to do everything
possible to destroy the peace talks.

34:06.480 --> 34:08.550
Fortunately, we managed to deal
with him today

34:08.550 --> 34:09.760
and prevent him from finding out

34:09.760 --> 34:11.820
such a big weakness of the Beifu Army.

34:18.550 --> 34:19.230
Yaoyao.

34:20.840 --> 34:21.440
Do you

34:22.960 --> 34:24.219
not hate Wuyi anymore?

34:25.000 --> 34:26.070
He is

34:26.070 --> 34:27.920
quite annoying most of the time

34:28.320 --> 34:30.320
and uses any means to achieve his goals,

34:30.320 --> 34:32.400
but there is one thing that is impeccable.

34:32.400 --> 34:32.920
What?

34:33.510 --> 34:35.000
He is the pillar of Ye.

34:36.030 --> 34:37.000
As long as he

34:37.190 --> 34:38.449
and the Beifu are here,

34:38.960 --> 34:40.620
we can live with some dignity.

34:42.150 --> 34:42.960
I respect him,

34:43.350 --> 34:45.480
and I will protect him when necessary.

34:46.540 --> 34:49.070
Mao, you have good taste in
choosing friends.

34:53.630 --> 34:55.880
Fortunately, all these terrifying things

34:55.880 --> 34:56.810
are about to end.

34:57.200 --> 34:58.660
You don't like this court,

34:58.920 --> 34:59.850
and neither do I.

35:00.840 --> 35:03.040
Yaoyao, after the peace talks are over,

35:03.440 --> 35:05.240
I will come and pick you up, okay?

35:21.000 --> 35:21.760
Anmin.

35:23.070 --> 35:25.030
I heard Wuyi fell off
a horse yesterday afternoon.

35:25.030 --> 35:25.830
Is it serious?

35:27.070 --> 35:28.480
The competition is coming soon.

35:28.480 --> 35:29.320
Be careful.

35:29.550 --> 35:31.610
Ruisheng has already come to see him.

35:31.790 --> 35:33.670
This is my usual medicine for wounds.

35:33.670 --> 35:36.530
It's highly effective
for healing and pain relief.

35:39.440 --> 35:40.630
Anmin, come with me.

35:49.360 --> 35:51.240
The stirrups still have flaws.

35:51.280 --> 35:52.710
They are not flexible enough.

35:52.710 --> 35:53.880
This is the improved blueprint I made,

35:53.880 --> 35:55.070
inspired by Master Yuan

35:55.070 --> 35:56.110
in the Beifu Army.

35:56.420 --> 35:58.320
If you are willing to give
me another chance,

35:58.320 --> 35:59.290
I will make it,

35:59.440 --> 36:00.770
and you can try it again.

36:01.510 --> 36:02.110
Forget it.

36:02.880 --> 36:03.630
Even if I can,

36:04.050 --> 36:05.910
Wuyi won't let me enter the field.

36:06.360 --> 36:08.030
I heard from Master Yuan

36:08.360 --> 36:09.490
that many years ago,

36:09.630 --> 36:11.160
Xiao Wuyi commissioned him

36:11.210 --> 36:13.540
to make a similar pair of stirrups
for you.

36:13.670 --> 36:15.510
I don't know what happened,

36:16.320 --> 36:17.000
but at least

36:17.670 --> 36:20.330
he once wanted you
to return to the battlefield.

36:32.430 --> 36:33.320
Careful!

36:33.510 --> 36:34.320
Let it go.

36:34.440 --> 36:35.550
He's a cripple.

36:36.160 --> 36:37.440
So what if I'm a cripple?

36:37.440 --> 36:38.770
Even with only one hand,

36:38.860 --> 36:40.120
I can still beat you up!

36:41.440 --> 36:42.040
You...

36:42.070 --> 36:42.720
Xiao Yao.

36:45.180 --> 36:45.710
Brother.

36:46.920 --> 36:48.510
It's time to return to the estate.

36:48.510 --> 36:49.150
Get lost!

36:59.230 --> 36:59.880
Brother!

37:01.840 --> 37:04.400
Do you really want
to compete in this match?

37:05.070 --> 37:06.150
I always thought

37:07.000 --> 37:08.280
Wuyi looked down on me

37:09.480 --> 37:12.480
and didn't want me to drag him
down in the Northern Border.

37:12.480 --> 37:13.340
But it turns out

37:13.550 --> 37:17.210
Mother was the one who didn't
want me to return to the battlefield.

37:17.590 --> 37:18.280
Yuanji,

37:18.960 --> 37:20.420
I just want to prove to you,

37:20.760 --> 37:21.630
to Mother,

37:22.150 --> 37:23.440
and to everyone else

37:23.630 --> 37:25.290
that I am not a useless person.

37:39.630 --> 37:42.190
You called me back
from the Northern Border

37:42.710 --> 37:44.710
to teach that girl?

37:46.320 --> 37:48.630
She does have some talent.

37:49.480 --> 37:51.360
But what's in it for me?

37:51.550 --> 37:53.010
Strong liquor, rice wine,

37:53.070 --> 37:54.360
brewed wine,
and bamboo leaf-green liqueur,

37:54.360 --> 37:55.560
which one do you want?

37:56.030 --> 37:57.190
I don't want to make a choice.

37:57.190 --> 37:58.050
I want them all.

37:58.550 --> 38:00.000
I also want Cangfeng Forge.

38:00.000 --> 38:00.730
Impossible.

38:01.630 --> 38:02.280
Xiao Wuyi,

38:03.030 --> 38:04.760
I've made weapons for you
for so many years.

38:04.760 --> 38:06.110
Can't I have

38:06.110 --> 38:07.190
my own armory?

38:08.670 --> 38:11.130
You're being so secretive about
that woman.

38:11.550 --> 38:13.280
I don't know what you're after.

38:13.320 --> 38:13.880
She?

38:15.510 --> 38:16.630
She has talent

38:17.280 --> 38:19.140
and the power to change the world,

38:19.320 --> 38:21.120
but she doesn't know it herself.

38:21.550 --> 38:23.150
I just don't want a pearl
to be covered in dust.

38:23.150 --> 38:23.960
Maybe

38:24.150 --> 38:27.550
her dream is just to be someone's wife

38:27.920 --> 38:29.440
and a child's mother.

38:29.800 --> 38:31.860
I didn't ask you to go to her right now.

38:32.430 --> 38:33.360
What do you mean?

38:34.030 --> 38:35.760
Are you treating me as a backup?

38:37.260 --> 38:39.120
So what if she loves someone else?

38:39.440 --> 38:40.800
Just snatch her back.

38:40.800 --> 38:42.200
Do you think this is a war?

38:42.510 --> 38:43.840
Since she sees me as a friend,

38:43.840 --> 38:44.800
I will be her friend.

38:44.800 --> 38:45.710
That's all.

38:47.440 --> 38:48.070
I hope

38:49.230 --> 38:50.490
if that day truly comes

38:51.880 --> 38:53.480
and she has various choices,

38:54.280 --> 38:56.340
making a decision is freedom itself.

38:56.960 --> 38:57.880
What about you?

38:59.110 --> 39:02.040
I am already someone
with no control over my own fate.

39:02.310 --> 39:04.170
I will never be one of her choices.

39:04.880 --> 39:07.630
That's not necessarily true.

39:08.500 --> 39:09.630
Let me calculate it.

39:10.320 --> 39:12.150
She's destined to marry three times,

39:12.150 --> 39:13.880
and her husband will die young.

39:14.760 --> 39:15.360
Oh no.

39:16.480 --> 39:19.540
You wouldn't happen to
be her first husband, would you?

39:21.840 --> 39:23.440
Did you really believe that?

39:24.130 --> 39:25.490
Well, Xiao Wuyi.

39:25.550 --> 39:26.800
Back at Jiuzhang Plain,

39:26.800 --> 39:29.440
I told you your life was in danger,
but you didn't believe me.

39:29.440 --> 39:31.320
Now, you believe this kind of bullshit?

39:31.320 --> 39:33.320
Naturally, I don't believe in fate.

39:33.710 --> 39:35.800
But if they are good words,

39:36.530 --> 39:37.860
I don't mind listening.

39:38.920 --> 39:41.000
Dying before thirty.

39:41.190 --> 39:42.230
How is that good?

39:42.480 --> 39:43.540
Why wouldn't it be?

39:43.800 --> 39:45.070
At least I won't die tomorrow,

39:45.070 --> 39:45.920
nor next year.

39:46.190 --> 39:47.320
How is that not good?

39:47.590 --> 39:48.070
Fine.

39:48.630 --> 39:49.430
You're crazy.

39:50.320 --> 39:52.440
Then, let me check your marriage bond.

39:52.440 --> 39:53.110
Let me see.

39:53.840 --> 39:54.400
No need.

39:55.110 --> 39:56.170
Come on, let me see.

39:57.480 --> 39:58.480
Don't be a coward.

40:01.150 --> 40:02.760
Just let me see.

40:03.620 --> 40:04.540
Seriously.

40:15.110 --> 40:17.110
It's raining. My leather!

40:18.360 --> 40:19.920
My Lady, go back inside.

40:19.960 --> 40:21.070
I'll handle this.

40:21.230 --> 40:22.290
Don't catch a cold.

40:24.150 --> 40:25.350
I'm not that fragile.

40:25.480 --> 40:26.680
Isn't this quite fun?

40:27.280 --> 40:28.030
Hurry up.

40:28.150 --> 40:29.440
We can't leave a single piece behind,

40:29.440 --> 40:31.100
or Anmin won't make it in time.

40:31.280 --> 40:32.840
But His Highness hasn't agreed yet.

40:32.840 --> 40:33.480
It's fine.

40:33.630 --> 40:36.760
Xiao Wuyi is tough on the outside
but soft inside anyway.

40:36.840 --> 40:38.280
Help me take these back first.

40:38.280 --> 40:38.840
Okay.

40:59.740 --> 41:03.910
♪ You know me and decided to
live and die together ♪

41:03.940 --> 41:07.770
♪ Believe in my persistence that
I won't run away ♪

41:07.980 --> 41:12.270
♪ You know I'm unyielding ♪

41:12.360 --> 41:15.520
♪ Burn the fire in my heart ♪

41:16.350 --> 41:19.520
♪ Sincere hearts remain as of old ♪
